{
  "texts": [
    "This paper uses a classification model to classify three types of pharmacological combinations: synergism, additive, and antagonistic.",
    "This guarantees that the medication combination is effective on the designated cell.",
    "Furthermore, we applied machine learning algorithms to predict the drug combination sensitivity score to enhance the results with real data.",
    "The experimental results pass different stages to achieve the required classification and prediction tasks.",
    "Starting with the preprocessing stage, the normalization, outlier removable, and data balancing were performed."
  ]
}